value.0: A Moonknight of Selune, whose armor glows softly like moonlight. The Moonknights are a highly militant order of soldier-priests devoted to The Moonmaiden. The branch stationed in Moonpier acts as an elite guard force under the command of the church.
This is a settlement guard insignia for the guard templates.
A member of the Moonpier Militia. They seem intent on their duties of protecting the town, wearing equipment that appears to be of high grade, glowing softly with an internal light.
